<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481423' id='t-481423'>realize that she might have had the baby.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486284' id='t-486284'>She might have placed for adoption.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489790' id='t-489790'>She might have told her parents 
and her partner -- or not.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494503' id='t-494503'>She might have felt relief and confidence,
even though you felt sad and lost.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500450' id='t-500450'>This is okay.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503723' id='t-503723'>Empathy gets created the moment we
imagine ourselves in someone else's shoes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509606' id='t-509606'>It doesn't mean we all have 
to end up in the same place.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514729' id='t-514729'>It's not agreement, it's not sameness
that pro-voice is after.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521207' id='t-521207'>It creates a culture and a society that 
