<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537551' id='t-537551'>instead of fear.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540386' id='t-540386'>And it generates the empathy that we need</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542600' id='t-542600'>to overcome all the ways
