<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557603' id='t-557603'>the more it spreads.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563149' id='t-563149'>So, last year I was pregnant again.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566253' id='t-566253'>This time I was looking forward 
